<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.5.3">
<l>tāmmō ruruṭṭit tayirney viḻuṅkiṭṭu</l>
<l>tāmō tavaḻvareṉ ṟāycciyar tāmpiṉāl</l>
<l>tāmō tirakkaiyā lārkkat taḻumpirunta</l>
<l>tāmōta rākoṭṭāy cappāṇi</l>
<l rend="indent">tamaraik kaṇṇaṉē cappāṇi.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Dāmodara who, having tipped the buttermilk and</l>
<l>Having gulped down curds and ghee, has welts, since the herdess</l>
<l>With a rope in her ringed hand tied him, thinking,</l>
<l>“Is he the one who crept [in here],” clap your hands;</l>
<l rend="indent">Lotus-eyed one, clap your hands!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
